{
  "title": "Thai-Sweet Egyptian Basil Tagine",
  "description": "A floral and gooey dish that blends the sweetness of Thai basil with the richness of Egyptian spices, perfect for a monsoon evening. This Ayurvedic-friendly recipe uses tamasic-friendly ingredients for a unique flavor experience.",
  "cuisine": "Egyptian",
  "diet": [
